Name: Tiki Man
About the game: Harness the legendary powers of the Tiki Man by chopping down the world's tallest tiki. Chop the tiki faces and avoid the hazardous tiki arms. Sounds easy? Think again my friend. 4 luscious tropical environments and 16 Tiki Men to unlock. Master your tiki chopping skills to earn high scores. Take the axe and chop the tiki as fast a you can! Checkout our new game KickAss Commandos! / If you like Tiki Man, also try Miner Mayhem! /
